		<title>Internet Court aims to become the legal infrastructure for agentic commerce</title>
		<link>https://contxto.com/en/inteligencia-artificial/internet-court-aims-to-become-the-legal-infrastructure-for-agentic-commerce/</link>
					<comments>https://contxto.com/en/inteligencia-artificial/internet-court-aims-to-become-the-legal-infrastructure-for-agentic-commerce/#respond</comments>
		
