		<title>Medellín as a hub for innovation and entrepreneurship in Latin America</title>
		<link>https://contxto.com/en/venture-capital-es/medellin-as-a-hub-for-innovation-and-entrepreneurship-in-latin-america/</link>
					<comments>https://contxto.com/en/venture-capital-es/medellin-as-a-hub-for-innovation-and-entrepreneurship-in-latin-america/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Ana Herazo]]></dc:creator>
